g.text: In this exercise you access data available in different file types. The data that you read in this exercise is stored in the "data" folder.
Access the data coming from two customer information systems in .table and .csv formats
Access the data on online orders and product prices stored on a database
Select the "TransactionsOnline" table on the database
Select the "ProductNrAndPrice" table on the database
(optional) Access the data on onsite purchases and the locations of the stores in .xlsx and .table formats
